# GLAW — environment template.  Copy to `.env` and set only what you use.
# The CORE firm (matters, pipeline, drafting, structured-format bookkeeping) needs
# NONE of these. Everything below is optional progressive enhancement.
#
# ⚠️  NEVER commit a real .env. It is git-ignored, and glaw-doctor [6/6] fails the
#     build if a live key or credential file ever lands in the tree.

# --- Google output (Sheets / Docs / Slides) ---------------------------------
# Authorized-user OAuth creds with spreadsheets + drive scopes.
# Used by: glaw-bank-ingest --format gsheet, glaw-publish
# Default location (no var needed): ~/.gcp/token.json
# GOOGLE_OAUTH_TOKEN=~/.gcp/token.json

# --- Bookkeeping PDF path (optional; structured formats + scanned PDFs need none) ---
# Non-tabular digital PDFs can route through a text LLM (opt-in).
# BSP_HYBRID_MODEL=ollama/llama3
# Image-only PDFs default to local Tesseract OCR ($0). To use a vision model instead:
# BSP_HYBRID_VISION_MODEL=ollama/minicpm-v

# --- Research / lookups (optional) ------------------------------------------
# Higher rate limits for the court scraper (juriscraper / CourtListener):
# COURTLISTENER_TOKEN=
# Nonprofit / IRS 990 lookups (glaw-exempt-org):
# PROPUBLICA_API_KEY=
